        " اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ  ۝ وَ مَنْ يَقْتُلْ مُؤْمِناً مُتَعَمِّداً فَجَزٰاؤُهُ جَهَنَّمُ ۝ قَالَ \"إِنْ جَازَاهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5172 - Hammad ibn Isa narrated from Abu Al-Safatij from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding the saying of Allah (swt), the Almighty and Majestic:\n\"And whoever kills a believer intentionally, his recompense is Hell\" (Surah An-Nisa 4:93).\nImam (as) said: \"If Allah (swt) chooses to punish him.\""
        ]
      }
